videos.headline: Pinckney makes a nice catch over his defender for Georgia State TD
videos.description: Dan Ellington puts it in the air to Sam Pinckney, who makes a nice catch over his Army defender for a 12-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pinckney makes a nice catch over his defender for Georgia State TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Army tricks Georgia State for a 16-yard touchdown
videos.description: Jalen Moy scores on the end-around to give Army a lead vs. Georgia State with a 16-yard strike.
